annotationA: 26S proteasome regulatory complex subunit p30; Endopeptidase activity. annotationB: 26S proteasome non-ATPase regulatory subunit 9; Acts as a chaperone during the assembly of the 26S proteasome, specifically of the base subcomplex of the PA700/19S regulatory complex (RC)
